<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.2.6">
<l>aṅkai yālaṭi mūṉṟunī rēṟṟaya ṉalarkoṭu toḻutētta</l>
<l>kaṅkai pōtarak kālnimirt taruḷiya kaṇṇaṉvan tuṟaikōyil</l>
<l>koṅkai kōṅkavai kāṭṭavāy kumutaṅkaḷ kāṭṭamā patumaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>maṅkai mārmukaṅ kāṭṭiṭu nāṅkūr vaṇpuru ṭōttamamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells Kaṇṇaṉ who, having arrived [incarnate],</l>
<l rend="indent">having received water in his palm for three feet [of earth],</l>
<l>While the Unborn [Brahmā] praised [him], worshipping with  flowers,</l>
<l rend="indent">and as the Ganges gushed effortlessly,</l>
<l>Granted mercy stretching his leg, is Vaṉpuruṭōttamam in Nānkūr,</l>
<l>Where silk cotton [bark] appear [like] breasts, lilies appear [like] lips,</l>
<l rend="indent">and ladies’ faces appear [like] large lotuses.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
